2F12%2F005858_ac67354c305212fe6e0434669e072098.jpg&h=260406d4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n睇完心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8496538554ac924e95d03cb131d47b035adbba","tid":197120,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"送飯盒到學校的女送貨員疑因食物阻街，遭數名食環署人員勒令將貨收起。她返回私家車準備驅車離開時，其中一名人員突強行打開車門不讓她離開，並大聲警告她不要開車。惟私家車三度慢速倒車，該人員聲稱被車門撞到致臀部受傷，爆粗責罵「哎呀死啦，X你老母，現在撞到我蘿柚痛」，指控送貨員襲擊公職人員，並吩咐同事拍片及召救護車。案件昨開審。<br />\n記者：戴國輝<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，以狂亂駕駛及妨礙公職人員執行職務罪拘捕被告章婉和（54歲），但章最終僅被票控不小心駕駛罪，她不認罪受審。案發於去年1月21日，食環署派員到九龍城延文禮士道民生書院對開巡查，<span style=\"color: red;\">案中聲稱被撞傷的56歲食環署助理小販管理主任陳介夫已於去年11月因心臟病發去世。</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"7f04cfa75315e1a7b571a2ffd3cb1151da325ec1","tid":197120,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"依啲就真係抵撚死喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bf8cc4636cb7f4396307dd0a5a638022e75e9b","tid":197120,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"呢d仆街抵死啦 人多蝦人少<br />\n死左都唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"61049bb06897bf90da268a87a9c2414b32fc2475","tid":197120,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fH2f73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fH2f73.jpg&h=733e0038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多得呢位司機拍片先唔洗俾食環狗任寫<br />\n<br />\n真係仗義每多屠狗輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3aaa982f0bfa19302c76bafedad6359240154fe","tid":197120,"uid":90247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep